<br>
&quot;Wouldn't have done any good.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;You should have knocked. You're being dericulous.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Rediculous.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;That's what I said. Dericulous. You're being stupid. Go back there, knock, say hello, and get a kiss. I think she'd kiss you.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;No,&quot; I said, and I knew as soon as the word crossed my lips it came out too harshly. &quot;You weren't there. You don't know. You don't know everything, Willow, and you know nothing about what happened between that girl and me.&quot; <br>
<br>
The pixie grew so angry her blue skin turned purplish. Then she flew off without a word. Well, without a word that should be said in the presence of ladies. <br>
<br>
&quot;She wouldn't have recognized me anyway,&quot; I said to no one at all. &quot;It was a lifetime ago.&quot; <br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
Siava and I, sitting by the water, talking under twilight in the Plane of Knowledge. Talking out deeply imbedded troubles. <br>
<br>
How do you put it into words? Sometimes I feel hollow inside, like someone could take a club and splinter me like a ceramic angel. <br>
<br>
But I try. Speaking has never been my strong point. I could never have been a bard. <br>
<br>
But when she leaves, I look at my hands, and they aren't shaking. And I smile. <br>
<br>
Thank you. <br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
I lost Pragger in the night, somewhere. <br>
<br>
The old rogue opened up a magical line of communication, pushed a &quot;hello&quot; into my ears, and I was never able to figure out how to reply. It was embarrassing. <br>
<br>
I lost Pragger in the night. Another old friend I passed by like a ghost. <br>
<br>
I'll find you again, you old scoundrel. I miss you. And I owe you an ale. <br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
&quot;You said you had one of the three,&quot; Siava says, and I smile. She's calling me on my own cryptic behavior. <br>
<br>
I tell her. And she proves me wrong.<br>
<br>
I smile. <br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
A quick whisper in my ear. A stranger's voice. Someone new. A compliment. <br>
<br>
A stranger on a strange night. <br>
<br>
***<br>
<br>
The ghost wolf pads up next to me and sighs.<br>
<br>
&quot;Where have you been?&quot; I ask No Moon, who sighs again. <br>
<br>
&quot;You're not dying, boy.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;What's that?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;You're not dying. I asked people in the know. So cut it out with this shaking business.&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;You don't sound so happy that I'm not dying.&quot; <br>
<br>
&quot;I'm dead, you're not, and you're not the only one who gets lonely, Lest-ye-forget. Go live your damned life before it's over.&quot; <br>
<br>
The wolf walks away. <br>
<br>
&quot;Thank you, old friend,&quot; I mutter. And I know, I know for certain, that he can hear me.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=647.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=647.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=647.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=647.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=647.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=647.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm62">In the Real Life News<option value="firionaviefrm58">Telegrams!<option value="firionaviefrm47">Guilds and Associations<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Day<option value="firionaviefrm23">Hero Heart Tavern<option value="firionaviefrm15">The Polli